  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/NetworkLink">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <rdfs:label>NetworkLink</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A physical or logical Link between Resources.

Usage notes:
- The organizational unit in charge of the Network Link (i.e. the Support team or Owner of the Network Link) can be set with the `noria:resourceManagedBy` property.
</rdfs:comment>
    <skos:example xml:lang="en">Optical fiber, L2TP connection, etc.</skos:example>
